#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"On October 7, we launched our donation campaign by explaining [[why "
"supporting Tails is more important than ever|news/2019-fundraiser]]. On "
"October 31, we summarized [[what we did in 2019 to make Tails easier to "
"adopt by new users|news/achievements_in_2019]]. Today we pass on to you our "
"plans for 2020."
msgstr ""
"El 7 d'octubre vam llançar la nostra campanya de donacions explicant [[per "
"què donar suport a Tails és més important que mai|news/2019-fundraiser]]. El "
"31 d'octubre, vam resumir [[què vam fer l'any 2019 per facilitar l'adopció "
"de Tails pels nous usuaris|news/achievements_in_2019]]. Avui us passem els "
"nostres plans per al 2020."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"But first, we are pleased that the donation campaign has been pretty successful so far. We received\n"
"around 50&#8239;000 € already, which is 69% more than last year.\n"
"Still, these good results are due to some large donations and\n"
"fewer people have been donating so far, 16% less than in 2018.\n"
"We hope that after reading this post many of you will consider <a\n"
"href=\"https://tails.net/donate/?r=plans2020\">donating to Tails</a>.\n"
msgstr ""
"Però primer, estem contents que la campanya de donacions hagi tingut bastant èxit fins ara. Hem rebut\n"
"uns 50&#8239;000€ ja, que és un 69% més que l'any passat.\n"
"Tot i així, aquests bons resultats es deuen a algunes grans donacions i,\n"
"fins ara, menys persones han donat, un 16% menys que el 2018.\n"
"Esperem que després de llegir aquesta notícia molts de vosaltres considereu <a\n"
"href=\"https://tails.net/donate/index.ca.html?r=plans2020\">donar a Tails</a>.\n"

